	* modules/dirkey/dirkey1.lisp: added impnotes doc for package LDAP
	* modules/fastcgi/fastcgi.lisp: added impnotes doc for package FASTCGI
	* modules/matlab/matlab.lisp: added impnotes doc for package MATLAB
