	* makemake.in (gen.lispbibl.c): fixed the sed(1) expression to work on
	solaris, darwin, openbsd, msys (gnu sed 3), cygwin&linux (gnu sed 4)
	Suggested by rouben@pc18.math.umbc.edu (Rouben Rostamian)

