	Make it possible again to do "make install" with a different user id
	even when Makefile is newer than cflags.h.
	* makemake.in (cflags.h.stamp): Renamed from cflags.h.
	(cflags.h): New rule.
	(clean4): Remove also cflags.h.stamp.

