	* lispbibl.d (unwind_back_trace): Remove unneeded #ifdef.
	* spvw_update.d (update_back_traces): Write if (bt != NULL), not just
	if (bt). Needed for Solaris C++.
	* spvw_garcol.d (gc_markphase): Likewise.

