	(check_symbol_special, check_funname_replacement):
	pass :FORM to ERROR-OF-TYPE SOURCE-PROGRAM-ERROR
	* eval.d (parse_dd, get_closure, eval1, fehler_eval_zuwenig)
	(fehler_eval_dotted, fehler_eval_zuviel): ditto
