	* init.lisp (specialized-lambda-list-to-ordinary): new function
	(*defun-accept-specialized-lambda-list*): enable just before the end
	(defun): use it when *DEFUN-ACCEPT-SPECIALIZED-LAMBDA-LIST* is non-NIL
