	* record.d (do_allocate_instance): Call FINALIZE-INHERITANCE instead
	of FINALIZE-CLASS. Fix GC-safety bug.
	(CLOS::%MAKE-INSTANCE): Call FINALIZE-INHERITANCE instead of
	FINALIZE-CLASS.

