	* eval.d (GOTO_ERROR): depend on DEBUG_BYTECODE, not DEBUG_SPVW
	(DEBUG_CHECK_BYTEPTR) [DEBUG_BYTECODE]: new macro
	(interpret_bytecode_): use it before a jump
