	(write, write-to-string): added :LINES arg
	* constsym.d: added :LINES, *PRINT-LINES* and SYS::*PRIN-LINES*
	* init.lisp: export *PRINT-LINES*
	* inspect.lisp (inspect): bind *PRINT-LINES* to *INSPECT-PRINT-LINES*
