	* stream.d (host_data_fetcher): accept an additional boolean argument.
	(publish_host_data): pass `resolve_p' to func
	(SOCKET-STREAM-PEER, SOCKET-STREAM-LOCAL): 1 optional argument
	* subr.d: ditto
