	* stream.d (check_float_eltype, READ-FLOAT, WRITE-FLOAT): New
	  functions.
	* lispbibl.d (c_float_to_FF, FF_to_c_float, c_double_to_DF)
	(DF_to_c_double): Declare always, not only if HAVE_FFI.
