1999-01-23  Bruno Haible  <bruno@linuix.math.u-bordeaux.fr>

	* debug.d (read_form): After EOF, call clear_input on istream, not on
	  the concatenated-stream. This fixes a strange REP loop behaviour on
	  Win32.

