	  SLOT-UNBOUND.
	(SYS::SET-SLOT-VALUE): Ignore the return values of SLOT-MISSING.
	(SLOT-BOUNDP, SLOT-MAKUNBOUND): Return only the first return value
	  of SLOT-MISSING.

